rget%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebroader%20studio%20styles%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMitch%20Stoltz%2C%20the%20IP%20litigation%20director%20for%20the%20Electronic%20Frontier%20Foundation%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20the%20latest%20model%20alone%20doesn't%20raise%20copyright%20issues%2C%20and%20that%20the%20distinction%20OpenAI%20makes%20between%20images%20generated%20from%20specific%20artwork%20and%20those%20generated%20from%20patterns%20the%20model%20learned%20is%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221764%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20AI-generated%20image%20of%20a%20magazine%20being%20held%20open.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e7ea343fecbb42897a2674%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221176%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChatGPT%20Images%202.0%20can%20generate%20images%20that%20appear%20to%20be%20photos%20of%20a%20physical%20magazine%20held%20open%20by%20a%20human.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20OpenAI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20output%20is%20substantially%20similar%20to%20something%20that%20the%20model%20was%20trained%20on%20or%20crawled%2C%20then%20there%20starts%20to%20be%20a%20copyright%20concern%2C%26quot%3B%20Stoltz%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20it's%20similar%20on%20the%20level%20of%20an%20idea%2C%20or%20just%20something%20that%20occurs%20in%20the%20world%2C%20or%20even%20a%20style%20or%20a%20vibe%20%E2%80%94%20generally%20speaking%2C%20that's%20not%20enough%2C%20and%20that's%20not%20a%20copy%20under%20copyright%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20is%20facing%20at%20least%20a%20dozen%20ongoing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-lawsuits-sam-altman-chatgpt-legal-challenges%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecopyright%20suits%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20writers%20and%20news%20outlets%2C%20including%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20and%20George%20R.R.%20Martin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20copyright%20issues%20are%20the%20same%20as%20if%20you%20were%20simply%20using%20Photoshop%2C%20a%20darkroom%2C%20or%20a%20human%20artist%20to%20make%20these%20kinds%20of%20replicas%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20issues%20for%20society%2C%20whether%20you%20call%20that%20ethical%20or%20political%20or%20whatever%2C%20are%20greater%20because%20it's%20easier%2C%20faster%2C%20and%20more%20available.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESocietal%20implications%20aside%2C%20at%20least%20we%20get%20a%20looksmaxxing%20oracle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-chatgpt-images-2-image-generator-fake-pictures-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776816036000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e7cb7b3fecbb42897a24ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-chatgpt-images-2-image-generator-fake-pictures-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22OpenAI%20unveiled%20its%20latest%20image%20generator%20model%2C%20ChatGPT%202.0%2C%20which%20can%20crawl%20the%20internet%20and%20create%20mockups%20of%20magazines%20and%20news%20articles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-chatgpt-images-2-image-generator-fake-pictures-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mamata%20Banerjee%20Claims%20Poll%20Body%20Denied%20Her%20Meeting%20In%20Collin%20Lane%20Area%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20slammed%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20commission%20denied%20her%20permission%20for%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20the%20Collin%20Lane%20area.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776815946000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2026-04%2Fiehds89s_mamata-banerjee_625x300_08_April_26.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cw