00%20Nvidia%20GPUs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20combination%20of%20Cursor's%20leading%20product%20and%20distribution%20to%20expert%20software%20engineers%20with%20SpaceX's%20million%20H100%20equivalent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-data-center-colossus-power-memphis-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EColossus%20training%20supercomputer%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20allow%20us%20to%20build%20the%20world's%20most%20useful%20models%2C%26quot%3B%20SpaceX%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BCursor%20has%20also%20given%20SpaceX%20the%20right%20to%20acquire%20Cursor%20later%20this%20year%20for%20%2460%20billion%20or%20pay%20%2410%20billion%20for%20our%20work%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECursor%20co-founder%20Michael%20Truell%20said%20in%20an%20X%20post%3A%20%26quot%3BExcited%20to%20partner%20with%20the%20SpaceX%20team%20to%20scale%20up%20Composer.%20A%20meaningful%20step%20on%20our%20path%20to%20build%20the%20best%20place%20to%20code%20with%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpaceX's%20partnership%20with%20Cursor%20comes%20at%20a%20pivotal%20moment%20for%20the%20company.%20In%20February%2C%20it%20acquired%20xAI%2C%20Musk's%20artificial-intelligence%20startup%2C%20broadening%20the%20rocket%20company's%20scope%20into%20AI%20infrastructure%20and%20software.%20Then%20in%20early%20April%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-spacex-ipo-space-stocks-lunr-fly-yss-pl-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpaceX%20confidentially%20filed%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20an%20IPO%2C%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20a%20potential%20public%20debut%20for%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuying%20Cursor%20would%20position%20SpaceX%20to%20compete%20more%20directly%20with%20frontier%20AI%20labs%20like%20Anthropic%20amid%20a%20heated%20race%20for%20more%20capable%20coding%20tools%20and%20AI%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXAI%20recently%20underwent%20shifts%20in%20its%20leadership%20structure%20as%20a%20slew%20of%20high-profile%20employees%2C%20including%20Musk's%2011%20original%20cofounders%2C%20left%20the%20startup.%20Musk%20said%20at%20a%20conference%20that%20Grok%2C%20xAI's%20chatbot%2C%20%26quot%3Bis%20currently%20behind%20in%20coding.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Business%20Insider%20reported%20that%20xAI%20was%20planning%20to%20provide%20Cursor%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-compute-cursor-ai-model-training-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecomputing%20power%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20sources%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECursor%2C%20founded%20in%202022%2C%20has%20emerged%20as%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20growing%20AI%20startups.%20Last%20November%2C%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20blogpost%20that%20it%20had%20reached%20%241%20billion%20in%20annual%20recurring%20revenue%20with%20a%20team%20of%20over%20300%20employees.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20company%20said%20it%20had%20completed%20a%20series%20D%20funding%20round%20at%20a%20%2429.3%20billion%20post-money%20valuation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20also%20been%20pushing%20to%20expand%20beyond%20code%20completion.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20it%20released%20its%20first%20agentic%20coding%20model%2C%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20effort%20to%20build%20tools%20that%20can%20take%20on%20more%20complex%20software%20tasks%20through%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20wanted%20to%20push%20our%20training%20efforts%20much%20further%2C%20but%20we've%20been%20bottlenecked%20by%20compute%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20startup%20said%20in%20a%20blog%2C%20announcing%20its%20SpaceX%20partnership.%20%26quot%3BWith%20this%20partnership%2C%20our%20team%20will%20leverage%20xAI's%20Colossus%20infrastructure%20to%20dramatically%20scale%20up%20the%20intelligence%20of%20our%20models.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-cursor-c