4%20everything%20from%20picking%20up%20your%20groceries%20to%20building%20furniture%20for%20you.%20It%20might%20seem%20silly%20at%20first%20%E2%80%94%20why%20would%20I%20pay%20someone%20to%20pick%20up%20my%20groceries%20if%20I%20am%20able%20to%20do%20it%20myself%3F%20The%20answer%20is%2C%20to%20save%20time.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexpensive-things-that-are-worth-the-money-2018-6%235-services-that-save-you-time-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20two%20financial%20experts%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20both%20agreed%20that%20spending%20on%20time-saving%20services%20is%20worth%20the%20splurge.%20Outsourcing%20small%20tasks%20is%20probably%20the%20closest%20you%20can%20get%20to%20actually%20getting%20back%20some%20hours%20in%20your%20day%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20it's%20a%20worthwhile%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EFrom%20meal%20delivery%20services%20to%20on-demand%20handymen%2C%20here%20are%20six%20great%20services%20that%20can%20help%20you%20complete%20your%20everyday%20tasks%20in%20less%20time%3A%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Csection%20data-slideshow-intro-content%3E%5Cn%3Csection%20data-slideshow-intro-content%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20list%20includes%20a%20Sponsored%20Product%20that%20has%20been%20suggested%20by%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiip_031219_amazon-home-services-20%26h%3Dbe30892d259a4bc0e72313dcf4ff752ccddb1f3e42460d7ea2c7fca8f59bee90%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42268%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Ftime-saving-service-taskrabbit-handy-amazon-home-services-instacart-thumbtack%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fdoordash.7zd4df.net%252Fc%252F196318%252F678987%252F10350%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDoorDash%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20it%20also%20meets%20our%20editorial%20criteria%20in%20terms%20of%20quality%20and%20value.*%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3