y%20window%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20when%20your%20food%20will%20be%20delivered%20right%20to%20your%20door.%20Delivery%20prices%20vary%20by%20store%2C%20but%20you%20can%20often%20snag%20free%20delivery%20deals.%20If%20you%20have%20other%20tasks%20to%20complete%20at%20home%2C%20this%20is%20a%20great%20way%20to%20save%20some%20time%20and%20get%20all%20the%20food%20you%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHandy%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22handy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c8813d62628982e38676a4e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHandy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffave.co%2F2tO2Ygo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMake%20a%20Handy%20appointment%20today%2C%20here%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20it%20is%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAn%20on-demand%20handyman%20and%20cleaning%20service.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20much%20it%20costs%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPrice%20varies%20based%20on%20task%2C%20zip%20code%2C%20and%20service%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20it%20works%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EPick%20the%20service%20you'd%20like%2C%20then%20the%20date%20and%20time%20when%20you'd%20like%20it%20done.%20Handy%20offers%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20services%20including%20home%20cleaning%2C%20home%20painting%2C%20furniture%20assembly%2C%20and%20housekeeping%2C%20among%20others.%20Handy%20recommends%20the%20amount%20of%20time%20you'll%20need%20to%20get%20different%20tasks%20done%20(for%20example%2C%20a%20cleaner%20will%20likely%20need%20more%20time%20to%20fully%20clean%20a%20large%20home%20than%20a%20small%20apartment).%20After%20filling%20out%20all%20of%20the%20information%2C%20Handy%20will%20send%20you%20a%20price%20quote.%20You%20can%20then%20book%20instantly%20%E2%80%94%20Handy%20appointments%20can%20be%20scheduled%20as%20early%20as%20one%20