urniture%2C%C2%A0%20bartend%20at%20your%20party%2C%20or%20even%20wait%20in%20a%20line%20for%20you.%20Once%20you%20choose%20the%20task%20you're%20interested%20in%2C%20you'll%20see%20a%20list%20of%20all%20of%20the%20qualified%20professionals%20aka%20%26quot%3BTaskers%26quot%3B%20in%20your%20area%20and%20how%20much%20they%20charge.%20TaskRabbit%20uses%20independent%20contractors%20who%20all%20set%20their%20own%20hourly%20rates%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can%20filter%20Taskers%20by%20their%20rates%2C%20number%20of%20positive%20reviews%2C%20and%20tasks%20completed%20to%20find%20the%20right%20person%20for%20the%20job.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20find%20the%20right%20Tasker%20for%20the%20job%2C%20schedule%20your%20appointment%20either%20online%20or%20on%20the%20app.%20You%20can%20usually%20find%20available%20appointments%20for%20the%20day%20of%2C%20or%20you%20can%20book%20further%20out%20%E2%80%94%20it%20really%20depends%20on%20the%20schedule%20of%20your%20Tasker.%20The%20day-of%20booking%20is%20particularly%20convenient%20in%20the%20case%20that%20you%20think%20you%20can%20do%20something%20yourself%2C%20but%20then%20realize%20you%20don't%20have%20the%20right%20tools%20or%20enough%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAmazon%20Home%20Services%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22amazon%20prime%20day%20home%20improvement%20tools%20deals%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c882ba4401d58024378625f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F2Ch2Nii%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBook%20an%20Amazon%20home%20%26amp%3B%20business%20service%20here%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20it%20is%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20selection%20of%20home%20services%20offered%20on%20Amazon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20much%20it%20costs%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPrice%20varies%20based%20on%20service%2C%20zip%20code%2C%20and%20other%20factors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20it%20works%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EJust%20when%20you%20thought%20the%20list%20of%20Amazon's%20products%20and%20services%20couldn't%20get%20any%20bigger%2C%20you%20can%20now%20count%20on%20the%20e-commerce%20behemoth%20to%20help%20you%20out%20with%20housekeeping%20services%2C%20furniture%20assembly%2C%20technology%20installation%2C%20and%20home%20maintenance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20ways%20to%20find%20the%20services%20and%20providers%20available%20in%20your%20area.%20You%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F2Ch2Nii%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esearch%20for%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%20you%20need%20specifically%20at%20any%20time%2C%20but%20you%20can%20also%20choose%20to%20add%20installation%20to%20many%20of%20your%20Amazon%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20pick%20the%20service%20you'd%20like%2C%20Amazon%20will%20give%20you%20an%20estimate%20based%20on%20your%20location%20and%20a%20few%20job-specific%20factors.%20Some%20services%20may%20not%20be%20offered%20in%20certain%20locations%20%E2%80%94%20it%20all%20depends%20on%20the%20pros%20that%20Amazon%20has%20available%20at%20any%20given%20time.%20Amazon%20is%20very%20transparent%20about%20exactly%20what%20the%20fee%20will%20get%20you%2C%20and%20provides%20information%20about%20how%20to%20change%20your%20appointment%20and%20what%20additional%20requests%20might%20be%20available%20as%20part%C2%A0%20your%20service.%20If%20you%20already%20have%20an%20Amazon%20account%2C%20using%20this%20service%20will%20be%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThumbtack%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22tumbtack%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c882f0269e11c038a18a962%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EThumbtack%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffig