%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20EPA's%20list%20of%20effective%20products%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDue%20to%20the%20novel%20coronavirus%2C%20many%20of%20these%20items%20are%20currently%20out%20of%20stock%2C%20so%20we'll%20do%20our%20best%20to%20keep%20this%20post%20updated%20with%20accurate%20in-purchase%20links.%20We've%20kept%20all%20links%20live%20in%20case%20the%20item%20becomes%20available.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20more%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-disinfecting-cleaner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20best%20disinfecting%20cleaners%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20homes%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20safe%20haven%20where%20we%20can%20relax%20and%20recuperate%20from%20what%20we've%20encountered%20out%20in%20the%20world.%20Unfortunately%2C%20we%20wind%20up%20bringing%20home%20the%20world%20and%20all%20its%20germs%20through%20dirty%20hands%2C%20shoes%2C%20clothing%2C%20and%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20your%20home%20looks%20clean%2C%20it%20may%20still%20harbor%20contaminants%20that%20could%20affect%20your%20health.%20Dr.%20Michael%20G.%20Schmidt%2C%20professor%20of%20microbiology%20at%20the%20Medical%20University%20of%20South%20Carolina%20and%20chair%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fasm.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Society%20of%20Microbiology's%20Council%20on%20Microbial%20Sciences%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20says%20that%20the%20best%20way%20to%20protect%20your%20family%20is%20to%20simply%20clean%20your%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Schmidt%20explains%20that%20after%20washing%20our%20hands%2C%20the%20next%20best%20way%20to%20protect%20your%20family%20is%20to%20wipe%20down%20countertops%2C%20doorknobs%2C%20light%20switches%2C%20and%20common%20surfaces%20with%20a%20microfiber%20cloth%20dampened%20in%20a%20solution%20of%20hot%20water%20and%20an%20all-purpose%20cleaner%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20nofollow%20nofollow%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipf_031320_how-to-disinfect-every-room-in-your-home-20%26h%3Dd3899e60ac43fe26d78e697adffd2691ef95918f12fa6d374c70b9875cdc6052%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42c8e%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fhow-to-disinfect-your-house%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgo.skimresources.com%252F%253Fid%253D35871X943606%2526amp%253Bxs%253D1%2526amp%253Burl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.target.com%25252Fp%25252Fmethod-cleaning-products-apc-french-lavender-spray-bottle-28-fl-oz%25252F-%25252FA-13531143%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20one%20from%20Method%3C%2Fa%3E%20twice%20per%20day.%20%26quot%3BThe%20slight%20abrasion%20of%20the%20microfiber%20cloth%20and%20the%20cleaning%20solution%20will%20lift%20and%20dilute%20any%20microbes%20that%20have%20settled%20on%20the%20surfaces%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr.%20Schmidt.%20%26quot%3BSince%20electronics%20don't%20hold%20up%20well%20to%20soap%20and%20water%2C%20use%20an%20alcohol%20wipe%20with%20at%20least%2070%25%20isopropyl%20alcohol%20to%20clean%20cell%20phones%2C%20remotes%2C%20and%20keyboards.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20difference%20between%20cleaning%20and%20disinfecting%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECleaning%20shouldn't%20be%20confused%20or%20used%20interchangeably%20with%20disinfecting.%20The%20former%20means%20you're%20removing%20germs%20but%20not%20killing%2C%20while%20the%20latter%20means%20you're%20actually%20killing%20them.%20This%20distinction%20is%20important%20because%20you%20might%20clean%20surfaces%20effectively%20but%20you%20might%20not%20be%20disinfecting%2C%20leaving%20germs%20and%20bacteria%20to%20fester%20and%20grow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisinfecting%2C%20if%20done%20correctly%2C%20will%20kill%20microscopic%20organisms%20so%20that%20they%20can%20no%20longer%20cause%20harm.%20However%2C%20Dr.%20Schmidt%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BDisinfecting%20cleaners%20can%20give%20a%20false%20sense%20of%20security%20if%20they%20are%20not%20used%20properly%20and%20are%20only%20necessary%20if%20someone%20in%20the%20household%20is%20ill.%26quot%3B%20The%20key%20areas%20to%20address%20are%20surfaces%20that%20are%20shared%20by%20family%20members%20and%20those%20that%20come%20in%20close%20contact%20with%20bodily%20fluids.%20If%20your%20windows%20are%20dirty%2C%20they%20aren't%20a%20big%20concern%20to%20your%20health%20but%20a%20doorknob%20touched%20after%20a%20sneeze%20can%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsc.edu%2Fstudy%2Fcolleges_schools%2Fmedicine%2Fabout_the_school%2Ffaculty-staff%2Fhorvath_joseph.php%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Joseph%20Horvath%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20associate%20professor%20of%20medicine%20in%20the%20Division%20of%20Infectious%20Diseases%20at%20the%20University%20of%20South%20Carolina%20Medical%20School%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20read%20labels%20and%20follow%20the%20directions%20on%20products.%20%26quot%3BProducts%20labeled%20as%20disinfectants%20will%20adequately%20kill%20viruses%20and%20bacteria%20if%20used%20correctly.%26quot%3B%20If%20the%20label%20promises%20to%20just%20%26quot%3Bsanitize%26quot%3B%20a%20surface%2C%20the%20fine%20print%20might%20say%20that%20it%20will%20kill%2099.9%25%20of%20the%20bacteria%2C%20but%20not%20mention%20if%20it's%20effective%20against%20viruses%20or%20fungi.%20You%20want%20to%20look%20for%20disinfectants%20as%20they%20can%20kill%20bacteria%2C%20viruses%2C%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20fungi%20when%20used%20properly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EHow%20to%20disinfect%20every%20room%20in%20your%20house%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20house-keeping%20expert%20with%20more%20than%2020%20years%20of%20experience%2C%20I%20have%20tested%20all%20the%20products%20listed%20here%20and%20gathered%20my%20best%20tips%20to%20help%20you%20disinfect%20the%20surfaces%20in%20every%20area%20of%20your%20home%20and%20slow%20the%20transfer%20of%20common%20communicable%20diseases.%20While%20many%20of%20the%20types%20of%20surfaces%20overlap%2C%20it's%20meant%20to%20be%20a%20comprehensive%20list%20of%20products%20you%20need%20to%20help%20keep%20your%20family%20healthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20due%20to%20the%20novel%20coronavirus%2C%20many%20of%20the%20items%20have%20stock%20issues%20or%20are%20heavily%20marked%20up.%20In%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclorox-wipes-supply-chain-complexity-keeps-company-from-meeting-demand-2020-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20interview%20with%20Reuters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Clorox%20CEO%20Benno%20Dorer%C2%A0said%20products%20like%20Clorox%20wipes%20won't%20be%20more%20readily%20available%20until%202021.%20We're%20actively%20researching%20and%20testing%20more%20products%20for%20their%20effectiveness%2C%20and%20we'll%20do%20our%20best%20to%20update%20this%20post%20with%20accurate%20purchase%20options%20as%20they%20become%20available.%20Your%20local%20brick-and-mortar%20stores%20might%20have%20more%20availability%20than%20online%20stores%2C%20but%20we've%20also%20kept%20the%20links%20live%20in%20case%20the%20item%20becomes%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20to%20disinfect%20a%20specific%20room%20in%20your%20house%2C%20click%20on%20the%20links%20below%2C%20otherwise%2C%20keep%20reading%20to%20see%20how%20you%20can%20disinfect%20your%20entire%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhow-to-disinfect-your-house%23how-to-disinfect-the-kitchen-1%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20disinfect%20the%20kitchen%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%