rget%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESustainable%20Forestry%20Initiative-certified%3C%2Fa%3E%20toilet%20paper%20remains%20strong%2C%20though%20it%20doesn't%20dissolve%20easily.%20But%2C%20despite%20the%20thick%20texture%2C%20it's%20sewer-%20and%20septic-safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuilted%20Northern%20guarantees%20that%20their%20rolls%20will%20fit%20your%20holder.%20If%20the%20rolls%20don't%20fit%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.quiltednorthern.com%2Ftoilet-paper-coupons%2Froll-extender%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20company%20will%20send%20you%20a%20free%20extender%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20toilet%20paper%3Cp%3EWe%20examined%20hundreds%20of%20expert%20and%20buyer%20reviews%20and%20ratings%20of%20many%20toilet%20paper%20brands%20and%20styles.%20The%20ones%20we%20chose%20to%20include%20in%20our%20guide%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20clean%20you%20down%20there%2C%20are%20septic-%20and%20sewer-system-safe%2C%20and%20have%20discernible%20softness.%20Here%20are%20some%20other%20factors%20to%20consider%20when%20shopping%20for%20toilet%20paper%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20standardization%20of%20toilet%20paper%20square%20or%20roll%20sizes%2C%20so%20words%20like%20%26quot%3Bmega%20roll%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bdouble%20roll%26quot%3B%20don't%20mean%20much.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20compare%20prices%2C%20look%20at%20the%20cost%20per%20square%20foot%20and%20the%20number%20of%20%26quot%3Bplys%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20layers%20of%20thickness.%20This%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftetrion.com%2Ftpcalc.php%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etoilet%20paper%20value%20calculator%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20great%20trick%20to%20bookmark%20if%20doing%20math%20in%20the%20toilet%20paper%20aisle%20isn't%20your%20strong%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20looking%20at%20costs%2C%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20you%20will%20use%20fewer%20sheets%20of%20three-ply%20than%20one-ply%20because%20of%20the%20superior%20cleaning%20and%20absorbing%20abilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToilet%20papers%20typically%20range%20from%201%20to%203%20ply%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20number%20of%20layers%20in%20each%20sheet%20of%20toilet%20paper%2C%20with%201%20ply%20being%20the%20thinnest%20and%203%20ply%20being%20the%20thickest.%20Some%20folks%20prefer%20our%20best%20budget%20option%2C%201-ply%20Scott%2C%20over%20our%20plush%203-ply%20pick%20from%20Quilted%20Northern%20since%20thicker%20toilet%20paper%20options%20sometimes%20create%20lint%20that%20people%20do%20not%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20down%20to%20deciding%20which%20is%20right%20for%20you%2C%20it%20is%20all%20based%20on%20personal%20preference%20and%20how%20you%20want%20your%20toilet%20paper%20to%20feel.%20A%20rule%20to%20follow%20is%20that%20a%20higher%20ply%20typically%20equals%20more%20comfort%2C%20whereas%20a%20thinner%20ply%20sacrifices%20comfort%20but%20is%20cheaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeptic%20safety%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou'll%20want%20to%20buy%20toilet%20paper%20that%20says%20%26quot%3Bseptic-safe%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20packaging.%20This%20notifies%20you%20that%20the%20toilet%20paper%20will%20cause%20less%20damage%20to%20your%20septic%20system.%20Septic-safe%20toilet%20paper%20breaks%20down%20quickly%20and%20into%20smaller%20pieces%20compared%20to%20non-septic-safe%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EProduct%20details%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20were%20doing%20our%20research%2C%20we%20found%20that%20there%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20buyer%20complaints%20about%20the%20rolls%20they%20ordered%20not%20being%20the%20same%20size%20as%20what%20they%20were%20used%20to.%20For%20this%20reason%2C%20when%20buying%20online%2C%20pay%20special%20attention%20to%20the%20sizes%20of%20the%20sheets%2C%20how%20many%20sheets%20are%20on%20a