ong%3EIs%20toilet%20paper%20bad%20for%20the%20environment%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Skene%2C%20natural%20climate%20solutions%20policy%20manager%20for%20the%20Natural%20Resources%20Defense%20Council%20(NRDC)%2C%20said%20that%20while%20some%20toilet%20papers%20are%20better%20than%20others%2C%20they%20all%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20the%20environment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NRDC%20publishes%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nrdc.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fissue-with-tissue-2021-scorecard.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20annual%20%26quot%3BIssue%20with%20Tissue%26quot%3B%20scorecard%20(pdf)%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20gives%20popular%20paper%20products%20a%20sustainability%20grade%20based%20on%20how%20the%20materials%20are%20sourced%2C%20the%20bleaching%20process%2C%20Forest%20Stewardship%20Council%20(FSC)%20certification%2C%20and%20other%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESkene%20said%20one%20of%20the%20major%20problems%20is%20that%20manufacturers%20rely%20on%20virgin%20forests%20for%20toilet%20paper%20production.%20Oftentimes%2C%20harvesting%20the%20forests%20infringes%20on%20indigenous%20rights%20and%20properties.%20And%20even%20bamboo%20is%20sometimes%20harvested%20unsustainably.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Chr%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20toilet%20paper%20is%20better%20for%20the%20environment%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20checking%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nrdc.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fissue-with-tissue-2021-scorecard.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENRDC%20scorecard%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Skene%20recommends%20looking%20for%20toilet%20paper%20certified%20by%20the%20FSC%20and%20made%20from%20post-consumer%20recycled%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Chr%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20can%20you%20reduce%20your%20toilet%20paper%20use%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20eco-friendly%20toilet%20paper%20brands%2C%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20forests%20and%20our%20environment%2C%20the%20less%20toilet%20paper%20we%20use%2C%20the%20better.%20Skene%20said%20that%20bidets%20are%20indisputably%20better%20for%20the%20environment%20than%20toilet%20paper%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESkene%20added%20that%20it%20takes%20more%20water%20to%20make%20toilet%20paper%20than%20you%20would%20use%20to%20clean%20yourself%20with%20a%20bidet.%20That%20doesn't%20even%20factor%20in%20the%20added%20waste%20of%20toilet%20paper%20and%20the%20effects%20of%20deforestation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20used%20bidets%20in%20my%20home%20and%20on%20the%20road%20for%20almost%20a%20decade%20and%20strongly%20recommend%20them.%20You'll%20still%20want%20to%20use%20some%20toilet%20paper%20to%20dry%20and%20spot-check%2C%20but%20having%20a%20bidet%20has%20drastically%20reduced%20my%20family's%20toilet%20paper%20use.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20are%20looking%20for%20a%20travel%20bidet%2C%20check%20out%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbrondell-gospa-travel-bidet-review%5C%22%3EBrondell%20GoSpa%20Travel%20Bidet%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%2C%20if%20you%20are%20looking%20for%20an%20at-home%20option%2C%20check%20out%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-bidet%5C%22%3Ebest%20bidets%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Chr%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20toilet%20paper%20do%20plumbers%20recommend%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EPlumbers%20recommend%201-ply%20toilet%20paper%20since%20it%20is%20thin%20and%20dissolves%20easily.%20While%20it%20might%20not%20be%20the%20most%20comfortable%2C%20it%20will%20protect%20your%20plumbing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Chr%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EHow%20long%20is%20a%20toilet%20paper%20roll%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20a%20roll%20of%20toilet%20paper%20contains%20200%20sheets%20or%20about%20900%20inches%20of%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20ar