nted%20in%20a%20medium-blue%20color%20from%20Benjamin%20Moore%2C%20and%20a%20bedroom%20is%20painted%20in%20a%20rust%20tone%20from%20Sherwin-Williams.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F627b94078f41d500187abc7d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22735%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Moore%3B%20Sherwin-Williams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20interior%20designers%20prefer%20Benjamin%20Moore%20or%20Sherwin-Williams%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20asked%20interior%20designers%20and%20color%20experts%20for%20recommendations%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-paint-colors-living-rooms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaint%20colors%20for%20living%20rooms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20offered%20a%20mix%20of%20the%20two%20companies%20but%20generally%20suggested%20more%20choices%20from%20Benjamin%20Moore.%20%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDifferent%20brands%20have%20different%20strengths%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20colors%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20color%20consultant%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famywax.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmy%20Wax%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I'm%20going%20more%20towards%20earthier%20grays%20and%20beiges%20and%20slate%20blues%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20look%20more%20towards%20Sherwin-Williams.%20With%20Benjamin%20Moore%2C%20sometimes%20they%20have%20a%20little%20bit%20brighter%20colors%2C%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20colors%20that%20are%20energized%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20to%20me%2C%20it's%20a%20matter%20of%20what%20I'm%20trying%20to%20accomplish%20as%20to%20what%20paint%20company%20I'm%20going%20to%20use.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EDoes%20Sherwin-Williams%20or%20Benjamin%20Moore%20offer%20better%20color%20matching%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTypically%2C%20I%20tell%20people%20to%20pick%20any%20color%20that%20they%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Travis%20Nolan%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oldcrowpainting.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOld%20Crow%20Painting%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Nine%20times%20out%20of%2010%2C%20he%20said%20both%20companies%20can%20match%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20explained%20that%20Benjamin%20Moore's%20Aura%20line%20seems%20a%20little%20trickier%20to%20get%20just%20right.%20Both%20Matt%20Kunz%2C%20president%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fivestarpainting.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFive%20Star%20Painting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Michael%20Camper%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmmprecisionpainting.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EM%26amp%3BM%20Precision%20Painting%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20Sherwin-Williams%20has%20superior%20color-matching%20software%20and%20mixer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EWhat%20brand%20lets%20me%20use%20just%20one%20coat%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ECamper%20said%20regardless%20of%20a%20brand's%20claim%20that%20it%20only%20needs%20one%20coat%2C%20you%20should%20do%20a%20second%20and%20prime%20your%20walls%20first.%20%26quot%3BPut%20two%20coats%20on%2C%20and%20you're%20guaranteed%20to%20get%20the%20highest%20quality%20finish%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EWhich%20brand%20is%20best%20for%20different%20climates%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20folks%20that%20like%20to%20use%20either%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstore.benjaminmoore.com%2Fstorefront%2Fus%2Fen%2Fcoating%2Fexterior-paints%2Fbenjamin-moore%2Fregal-select-exterior-paint%2Fregal%2Fp%2FRSE%2520LL%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERegal%20Select%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffili