ty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EWhat%20paint%20should%20you%20use%20if%20you're%20hiring%20professionals%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EKunz%20and%20Camper%20both%20said%20if%20your%20painting%20crew%20is%20pushing%20for%20a%20particular%20brand%20and%20type%20of%20paint%2C%20it's%20because%20they%20know%20how%20to%20get%20the%20best%20results%20with%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20find%20is%20like%20certain%20crews%20will%20get%20very%20used%20to%20using%20one%20of%20the%20types%20of%20paints%2C%20and%20they'll%20lean%20towards%20it%20because%20they%20know%20just%20without%20even%20thinking%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kunz.%20%26quot%3BThey%20know%20the%20coverage%20rate.%20They%20know%20the%20right%20nap%20roller%20to%20use%20%E2%80%94%20everything%20that%20they%20need%20for%20that%20specific%20type%20of%20paint.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECamper%20likes%20using%20certain%20products%20over%20and%20over%20for%20the%20same%20reason.%20%26quot%3BI%20become%20familiar%20with%20its%20characteristics%2C%20the%20way%20it%20flows%2C%20what%20the%20dry%20time%20is%2C%20whether%20it's%20more%20apt%20to%20run%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20everyone%20we%20spoke%20with%20also%20suggested%20using%20higher-quality%2C%20more%20expensive%20paint.%20With%20a%20cheaper%20paint%2C%20%26quot%3Bif%20you%20hire%20a%20professional%20painter%2C%20and%20you%20want%20a%20good%20job%20done%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20end%20up%2C%20generally%2C%20using%20more%20product%20to%20cover%20with%2C%20so%20it's%20going%20to%20cost%20them%20more%20in%20labor%2C%26quot%3B%20Camper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaterials%2C%20including%20paint%2C%20make%20up%20about%2010%25%20of%20the%20total%20cost%2C%20so%20it%20makes%20more%20sense%20to%20save%20on%20labor%20if%20you%20can%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EWhat%20brand%20is%20best%20for%20DIYers%3F%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20painting%20yourself%2C%20the%20price%20calculation%20will%20be%20a%20little