on%20the%20customer%20service%20between%20Benjamin%20Moore%20and%20Sherwin-Williams.%20It%20seems%20to%20depend%20heavily%20on%20the%20managers%20and%20employees%20at%20individual%20stores.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EColors%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20think%20that%20Benjamin%20Moore%20offers%20better%20colors%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Camper.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20you're%20going%20to%20go%20with%20something%20vibrant%2C%20like%20a%20dark%20red%20or%20royal%20blue%20or%20something%20like%20that%2C%20Benny%20Moore%20is%20probably%20going%20to%20be%20a%20better%20option.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EColor%20samples%2C%20visualizers%2C%20and%20consulting%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Sherwin%20Williams%20ColorSnap%20Visualizer%20Tool%20and%20the%20Benjamin%20Moore%20Personal%20Color%20Viewer%20Tool%20showing%20the%20same%20kitchen%20painted%20in%20similar%20colors%20from%20each%20brand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F627b89fbdd983300191c89c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Taylor%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20thousands%20of%20colors%20to%20choose%20from%2C%20picking%20just%20one%20(or%20a%20whole%20palette)%20can%20be%20overwhelming.%20Both%20Sherwin-Williams%20and%20Benjamin%20Moore%20have%20ways%20to%20help%20you%20find%20the%20right%20one.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EColor%20chips%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAfter%20picking%20a%20color%20family%20or%20specific%20hue%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20start%20comparing%20different%20shades%20to%20each%20other.%20%26quot%3BColor%20chips%20are%20the%20best%20way%20to%20help%20narrow%20down%20the%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20Sue%20Wadden%2C%20director%20of%20color%20marketing%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sherwin-williams.com%2F%5C%22%20ta