303%2Fnon-profit-organisations-helping-conflict-affected-communities-india-manipur-kashmir-pahalgam-attack%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecentres%20where%20people%20are%20being%20sheltered%3C%2Fa%3E%20until%20the%20situation%20eases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-3-1757073678.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Across%20Punjab%2C%20gurudwaras%2C%20schools%2C%20and%20other%20public%20institutions%20have%20been%20turned%20into%20relief%20camps%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-3-1757073678.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-3-1757073678-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-3-1757073678-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-3-1757073678-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-3-1757073678-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496947%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAcross%20Punjab%2C%20gurudwaras%2C%20schools%2C%20and%20other%20public%20institutions%20have%20been%20turned%20into%20relief%20camps%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20heartwarming%20to%20see%20the%20boundaries%20of%20religion%20blur%20as%20people%20of%20all%20faiths%20come%20together%20to%20distribute%20the%20material.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20see%20volunteers%20of%20all%20faiths%20who%20have%20been%20working%20day%20and%20night%20to%20help%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harmeet%20shares.%20He%20tells%20the%20story%20of%20an%20elderly%20man%20whom%20they%20r